		<node ID="ID_783173104" LINK="https://docs.unity3d.com/Manual/AnimationGlossary.html" TEXT="Unity - Manual: A Glossary of animation terms">
			<node ID="ID_612949425" TEXT="Each state references an Animation Blend Tree or a single Animation Clip. More info See in Glossary: A graph controlling the interaction of Animation States. Each state references an Animation Blend Tree or a single Animation Clip. Animation Blend Tree Used for continuous blending between similar Animation Clips based on float Animation Parameters." />
