		<node ID="ID_170809787" LINK="https://www.studica.com/blog/game-design-tutorial-blend-trees-unity" TEXT="Game Design Tutorial: How to Use Blend Trees in Unity ">
			<node ID="ID_496966977" TEXT="A blend tree is much like a normal animation transition. In an animation transition you are going from one animation and transitioning into a different animation. A blend tree however allows blending animations together using variables. Blend trees are commonly used for things like character movement." />
