		<node ID="ID_955358039" LINK="https://stackoverflow.com/questions/4948322/fundamental-difference-between-hashing-and-encryption-algorithms" TEXT="Fundamental difference between Hashing and Encryption ">
			<node ID="ID_1172941103" TEXT="Hashing. Hashing is another cryptography technique in which a data once converted to some other form can never be recovered back. In Layman&#8217;s term there is no process called de-hashing. There are many hash functions to do the job such as sha-512 md5 and so on. If the original value cannot be recovered then where do we use this? Passwords!" />
