		<node ID="ID_971146989" LINK="http://groups.umd.umich.edu/cis/course.des/cis350/hashing/WEB/HashHelp.htm" TEXT="Hashing Animation Tool Help - University of Michigan">
			<node ID="ID_1755629372" TEXT="This algorithm requires two hash tables. The hash function is based on the number of buckets in the primary hash table. All home addresses calculated by the hash function refer to the primary table. Data is inserted in the overflow table only if the home address in the primary table is full." />
