			<node ID="ID_1546948323" TEXT="In a line sequential file each record in the file is separated from the next by a record delimiter. Figure 14-1: Line Sequential Structure. For files created on UNIX systems the default record delimiter is the Line Feed character specified by the single byte xOA." />
			</node>
